# ║ Path(_(exp), * imaginary**odd -> imaginary * imaginary**even -> real * b**imaginary -> !imaginary if exponent is an integer multiple of i*pi/log(b) * imaginary**real -> ? * positive**real -> real * negative**integ) over Any ║
